    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "connection or meaning... i dont know. it feels like a joke. even if i find something small, it just goes away. then it's just back to the void. it's like trying to fill a bucket with holes in it. why even bother struggling to keep it full when we know it's just gonna be empty again?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
